  %p
    If you've never heard of Kingdom Builder before, then you can check out its currently ongoing (until March 8th)
    = link_to("Kickstarter Page", "https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/queengames/kingdom-builder-marshlands")
    to find out more about the game. I will do my best to keep this thing updated as new releases/expansions come out, and I'm proud to say that it is equipped with quite a few ranomization options to use! If you're interested, you can play around with it over here. Thanks as always for checking in! Maybe the next one will be more relevant to you people... but I make no promises.
